1.title: Dinner 1
1.plot: Kitchen Circus - reality web series Episode 1. Three home cooks make one course for 45 diners. Award winning Chef Thierry Rautureau guides contestants from cooking through service. Will it be Angel, Siiri or Beth who makes the diner's favorite course? Celebrity Guests include: Tom Douglas (Seattle Restaurateur), Steve Scher (NPR Radio Host), Marty Riemer (Radio Host).

2.title: Dinner 2
2.plot: Kitchen Circus - reality web series Episode 2. How will Atina, Myrissa and Chris do preparing dinner for 45 judges? Chef Thierry Rautureau along with celebrity guests Rachel Belle (KIRO radio host) and Steve Scher (NPR Radio host) critique the dinner courses.

3.title: Dinner 3
3.plot: Kitchen Circus web series - Dinner 3. Will it be Peter, Erina or Christine who fills the last slot in the Kitchen Circus Finale? Chef Thierry Rautureau along with celebrity guests Jason Wilson (Chef/Owner of Crush), Maria Hines (Chef/Owner of Tilth, Golden Beetle and Agrodolce), and Steve Scher (NPR Radio Host) decide who will move on to the Finale.

4.title: Dinner 4
4.plot: Kitchen Circus - reality web series Episode 4 - Finale. The diners have chosen, Chef Thierry Rautureau announces the winner of Kitchen Circus. Celebrity Guests include former Rover's sous chef Adam Hoffman (Chef/Owner of Adams NW Bistro & Brewery), Steve Scher (NPR Radio host), and Jamie Peha (food & wine marketing expert).

imdb.title: Kitchen Circus
synopsis: A reality web series hosted by award winning Chef Thierry Rautureau. Nine home cooks with no professional kitchen experience are thrown into the big time competing on Kitchen Circus. Each contestant makes one course of a three course meal in a professional 4 star restaurant for a 45 dinner guests. The diners each night are the judges and vote on 3 criteria; Taste, Presentation and Creativity. The votes are tallied at the end of each meal, and a winner is chosen to move on to the finale at the end of the season. Celebrity guest judges who critique the meals include Tom Douglas (Seattle Restauranteur), Maria Hines (Chef & Owner of Tilth, Golden Beetle, Agrodolce), Jason Wilson (Chef & Owner of Crush) and many more.Sponsored by Charlie's Produce, Gene Juarez, Le Creuset and OpenTable. Produced by MAD Valley Productions
